column1: Breaking! #NewYorkCity Launches #COVID19 Pet Hotline To Provide Support For Animals Of Residents Affected By The #Coronavirus The Pet Hotline operators can be reached at (877) 204-8821, from 8:00am to 8:00pm EST daily.
